                 </p>
                 <Button onClick={() => handleGenerateEvaluation(selectedStudent)} isLoading={isGenerating} className="w-full py-5 rounded-[1.25rem] text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-xl shadow-primary-500/10">
